rows.label: qst200910_msg001
rows.name: You came to rescue me? I'm grateful...

rows.label: qst200910_msg002
rows.name:
Anyway, it's dangerous
here. Let's go back to
the Saets Lumber Company.

rows.label: qst200910_msg004
rows.name:
Don't worry, I'm not injured. I
can stand and walk on my own.

rows.label: qst200910_msg005
rows.name:
Everyone must be worried, so we
should let them know I'm safe soon.
